        <h2>Get your potential customers in your store.</h2>
        <p>Using Apple's new app <a href="http://www.apple.com/ios/ios6/#passbook">Passbook</a>.  We allow you to offer your customers deals on products.  Not only does a deal allow them to get a better discount, it also alerts them when they are near your store.</p>
