	    <p class="marketing-byline">How we deliver deals to your customers for use in your retail stores</p>

		<img src="/assets/ios_screenshot.png" width="320px" class="img-polaroid">
		<legend class="marketing-byline" style="font-size: 15px;">An Example Coupon in Passbook</legend>
		<p>In the image above, you can see a example coupon.  In this case it is for a store called "Joe's Clothes".  When a user adds a item to their MightBuy account and you offering a deal on it (in your retail store), they will be prompted to add the pass to their phone.  You can then scan the coupon or we can show the barcode in plain text so you can verify it is correct</p>
	
		<br>
		<br>
		<br>
